Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.39,0:00:59.88,note1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs46\fsp3\fad(900,1600)}机动战士高达UC 独角兽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.69,0:01:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑色…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.08,0:01:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,独角兽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.70,0:01:15.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友军？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.12,0:01:21.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.48,0:01:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃 巴纳吉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.42,0:02:06.70,note1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38\fsp3\fad(900,1100)}第五话 黑色独角兽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.98,0:03:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舱门无法打开
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.24,0:03:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用我给你们的解密代码
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.25,0:03:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把他给我揪出来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.68,0:03:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你怎么在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.17,0:03:32.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那台黑色独角兽是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.27,0:03:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 你说报丧女妖？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.27,0:03:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(692,659)\fnarial\fs26\b0\fsp1}Banshee
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.53,0:03:39.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一句两句跟你说不清
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.69,0:03:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.02,0:03:42.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.22,0:04:02.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是家族问题
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.01,0:04:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对别人的家务事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.86,0:04:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,军队也不能擅加干涉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.28,0:04:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家族？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.79,0:04:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不怕被你笑话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.73,0:04:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他 巴纳吉·林克斯是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.10,0:04:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的父亲 前代家主
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.68,0:04:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡帝亚斯·毕斯特 和情妇生下的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.38,0:04:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此 请不要刨根问底
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.99,0:04:24.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴纳吉是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.05,0:04:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舱门打开
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.51,0:04:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,系统拒绝外界接触
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.66,0:04:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今保持完全静默
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.26,0:04:56.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.42,0:04:57.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据推测
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.50,0:05:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是巴纳吉·林克斯对其加密
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.25,0:05:02.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有他的认证
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.00,0:05:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就无法得到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.36,0:05:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉普拉斯系统开示的新坐标
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.17,0:05:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是血统作怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.92,0:05:12.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.25,0:05:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…不
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.74,0:05:17.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他出生时
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.57,0:05:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还在寄宿制学校
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.97,0:05:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到那少年是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.14,0:05:23.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倔脾气像极了他父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.22,0:05:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让她出面说服也许更好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.69,0:05:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥黛丽·本
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.73,0:05:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相当不错的化名
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.18,0:05:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遣送我来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.61,0:05:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经过罗南·马瑟纳斯议长的许可吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.57,0:05:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是自然
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.48,0:05:55.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗南议长与我们有着相同的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.31,0:06:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们将封印拉普拉斯之盒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.42,0:06:10.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殿下此行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.13,0:06:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不外乎为了这个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.73,0:06:15.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用多久 盒子的钥匙…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.65,0:06:18.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,独角兽高达将运抵这艘迦楼罗号
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.65,0:06:18.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(819,659)\fnarial\fs26\b0\fsp1}Garuda
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.13,0:06:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前 年轻的驾驶员
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.40,0:06:23.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会充当它的守护者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.14,0:06:26.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殿下对那人不陌生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.13,0:06:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴纳吉·林克斯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.17,0:06:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他对昨天战斗中获得的坐标进行加密
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.79,0:06:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私自藏匿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.16,0:06:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娼妇之子继承了父亲愚蠢的妄想
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.33,0:06:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在让人伤透了脑筋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.50,0:06:44.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴纳吉是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.57,0:06:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位大人的…？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.32,0:06:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可愿意与我联手？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.02,0:06:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,密涅瓦殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.28,0:07:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我说服巴纳吉？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.00,0:07:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会亏待你的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.37,0:07:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括追随你的吉翁残党
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.17,0:07:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 首先
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.47,0:07:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请交还玛莉妲·库鲁兹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.92,0:07:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莉妲中尉…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.79,0:07:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,璞露12在我们麾下工作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.98,0:07:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是出于她的意愿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.35,0:07:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明强行进行再调试
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.70,0:07:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 完全没错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.21,0:07:27.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像新吉翁做过的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.56,0:07:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,造出那种可悲生物的并不是我们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.07,0:07:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是解放了她的内心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.65,0:07:40.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赐予她复仇的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.63,0:07:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,复仇？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.86,0:07:42.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.03,0:07:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向造就她的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.35,0:07:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向被男性理论支配的世界复仇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.68,0:08:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保密也得有个限度
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.44,0:08:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则没法保证舰船安全
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.03,0:08:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都能在船上撒野 这仗还怎么打！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.37,0:08:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们现在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.73,0:08:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须服从参谋总部指示
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.19,0:08:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,配合财团也是其中一环
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.06,0:08:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隆德·贝尔队任务不变
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.76,0:08:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,调查入侵地球的新吉翁军舰船
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.14,0:08:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是本舰的第一要务
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.31,0:08:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.45,0:08:34.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情势发生了变化 这点无法否认
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.37,0:08:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即刻使用飞船
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.26,0:08:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将捕获的高达型机体运往太空
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.10,0:08:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成之后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.19,0:08:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕斯特财团就撤离本舰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.71,0:08:50.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家也许会有想法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.54,0:08:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请严格自律切忌轻率妄动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.94,0:08:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解散
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.78,0:09:01.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说运往迦楼罗的物资
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.86,0:09:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清一色贵宾专用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.14,0:09:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说罗氏商会的情报准确
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.48,0:09:09.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能和他谈谈吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.26,0:09:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方答应得很痛快
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.26,0:09:13.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心被窃听
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.84,0:09:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这还是我们的船吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.98,0:09:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想和你谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.93,0:09:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.33,0:09:40.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫布莱德·诺亚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.13,0:09:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这艘拉·凯拉姆的舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.30,0:09:47.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说审讯官也拿你没辙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.25,0:09:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人和机体一样保持沉默吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.59,0:09:56.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可难倒了我们的技师
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.19,0:09:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都不能看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.21,0:10:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它如果泄露出去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.17,0:10:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里又会变成战场
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.17,0:10:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,许多人会死
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.09,0:10:07.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛妮小姐就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.23,0:10:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事 不想说的话不说就是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.95,0:10:15.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是自己逃出那艘伪装货船的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.23,0:10:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说逃出不太准确
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.83,0:10:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想…是他们放我走的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.88,0:10:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那场作战
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.30,0:10:26.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船长也并不赞同
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.73,0:10:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.62,0:10:31.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那艘船的行动中可以看出
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.88,0:10:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们没把你当俘虏对待吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.71,0:10:39.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有随意行动的自由？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.48,0:10:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.44,0:10:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少没有联邦说的 那种敌人的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.84,0:10:47.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.48,0:10:49.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能因为我不是军人…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.29,0:10:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不习惯区分敌我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.16,0:10:56.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 船上的气氛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.96,0:10:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也让我感觉没必要！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.49,0:11:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.85,0:11:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.06,0:11:05.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.78,0:11:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.69,0:11:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的眼中有一种力量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.17,0:11:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一种逆境中成长的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.21,0:11:18.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要不放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.69,0:11:20.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必能抓住机会
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.73,0:11:23.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我哪里…有那种力量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.02,0:11:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全是偶然
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.99,0:11:27.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐上独角兽也好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.77,0:11:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被关在这里也好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.44,0:11:30.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是这样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.48,0:11:36.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时 遇见高达也许是偶然
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.45,0:11:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前所有的高达驾驶者们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.84,0:11:40.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无一例外都是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.35,0:11:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 是否坐上高达取决于自己
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.37,0:11:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能说是偶然
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.50,0:11:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说错了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.54,0:11:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初 是什么让你决心坐上高达的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.48,0:12:03.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想救一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.66,0:12:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥黛丽·本…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.20,0:12:11.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家叫她密涅瓦·扎比
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.12,0:12:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,属实吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.24,0:12:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷比尔将军号出动了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.24,0:12:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(560,659)\fnarial\fs26\b0\fsp1}General Revil
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.76,0:12:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说试航中接到参谋部直接命令
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.05,0:12:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,显然是执行机密任务
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.35,0:12:33.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标是…拟·阿伽玛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.81,0:12:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.06,0:12:37.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是钓罗南议长上钩的饵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.94,0:12:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知情者必须死
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.85,0:12:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕斯特财团与参谋总部也算各让一步
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.67,0:12:46.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您打算怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.69,0:12:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷比尔将军号是地球舰队重建的关键
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.00,0:12:52.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被它盯上的话 拟·阿伽玛不堪一击
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.15,0:12:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您如果不方便直接联系
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.97,0:12:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们罗氏商会可以代为转达危险…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.10,0:13:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩托琪卡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.32,0:13:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想联系黑袖章的伪装货船
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.20,0:13:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.56,0:13:07.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对周旋于联邦和新吉翁的罗氏商会
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.99,0:13:08.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信不难做到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.24,0:13:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您当真吗 布莱德舰长？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.74,0:13:14.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交涉人选我已经有了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.30,0:13:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过可能有点讨厌吉翁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.68,0:13:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对你们也不是件坏事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.09,0:13:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 可以说是千载难逢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.54,0:13:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.30,0:13:30.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉普拉斯的钥匙如果被运走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.00,0:13:32.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,财团那伙人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.18,0:13:35.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会把你们的公主一起送上太空
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.37,0:13:37.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时候想动手也难
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.57,0:13:41.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么让我相信你们？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.48,0:13:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,财团和参谋们勾结
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.52,0:13:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对军队指手画脚发号施令
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.97,0:13:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有前线指挥官看不顺眼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.53,0:13:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又有财团的死对头罗氏商会
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.51,0:13:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们不担心盒子里放着什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.61,0:14:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是不想看到联邦和财团勾肩搭背
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.77,0:14:07.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为此不惜利用新吉翁？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.77,0:14:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船长…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.40,0:14:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劳驾准备一台飞行踏板
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.55,0:14:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽量安排
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.90,0:14:16.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来游击队有游击队的办法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.84,0:14:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 我们的人手略显单薄
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.84,0:14:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算出其不意 夺回公主
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.96,0:14:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没法脱身也是徒劳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.44,0:14:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始我就说这是联合作战！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.89,0:14:30.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,援军自然会有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.74,0:14:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且那艘船 你们一定不会陌生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.25,0:14:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.00,0:14:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在这种情况 必须先静下心来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.59,0:14:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奉命原地待机近20天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.42,0:14:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有烦躁情绪是人之常情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.50,0:14:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 作为各部门之长
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.89,0:14:59.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还须时刻保持镇定…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.21,0:15:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.37,0:15:06.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是急电
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.92,0:15:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.83,0:15:40.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看那孩子的直觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.16,0:16:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去迦楼罗为什么还带机师？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.72,0:16:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道上头在想什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.55,0:16:08.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利迪少尉！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.82,0:16:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥黛丽在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.34,0:16:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不是一起去地球了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.21,0:16:14.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她现在在哪儿？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.83,0:16:16.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利迪先生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.79,0:16:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借他说句话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.13,0:16:33.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉哟当心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.49,0:16:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球上摔跤会受伤哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.88,0:16:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不懂事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.90,0:16:43.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这艘船上他说了算
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.60,0:16:49.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥黛丽？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.71,0:16:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.64,0:16:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,移送迦楼罗的途中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.18,0:16:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑袖章的葛兰雪号将实施营救
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.75,0:16:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,协助他们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.33,0:17:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,返回太空
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.97,0:17:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与前来接应的拟·阿伽玛号汇合
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.01,0:17:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除此之外
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.17,0:17:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有让盒子远离阴谋的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.75,0:17:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也无法营救她
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.27,0:17:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能做到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.01,0:17:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.63,0:17:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能做的只有这些
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.01,0:17:23.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与过去的高达驾驶者一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.94,0:17:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愿意相信你也是被高达选中的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.12,0:17:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次从结果看 一切都是必然
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.02,0:17:37.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论好…与坏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.14,0:17:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布莱德舰长…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.88,0:17:41.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来就看你的了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.77,0:17:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别被情况吓倒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.85,0:17:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿出击退绝望的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.50,0:17:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.16,0:17:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高达驾驶者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.82,0:18:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是新人类的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.72,0:18:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥黛丽…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.15,0:18:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.27,0:18:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须向你的自尊心表示敬意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.59,0:18:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但自尊同样可以致人于死地
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.05,0:18:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懂吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.94,0:18:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才的举动
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.89,0:18:49.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲手夺走了追随你的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.56,0:18:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉翁幸存者们的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.59,0:18:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夺走了他们与毕斯特财团共存的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.93,0:18:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.79,0:19:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为自尊心杀男人是女人的专利
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.28,0:19:04.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝你成长为个好女人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.34,0:19:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把巴纳吉·林克斯那小子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.03,0:19:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当作食粮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.61,0:19:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴纳吉…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.12,0:19:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长刚才说啥了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.92,0:19:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别牵连咱们就好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.62,0:19:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公子哥知道吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.57,0:19:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 他也被排除在外了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.40,0:19:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以布莱德舰长的性格
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.55,0:19:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么也别大惊小怪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.63,0:19:37.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利迪少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.54,0:19:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,独角兽拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.33,0:19:43.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保护它对你也有益处
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.60,0:19:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲的想法是父亲的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.31,0:19:48.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还年轻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.81,0:19:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信自己的判断
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.95,0:19:52.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.19,0:19:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用你说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.78,0:19:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,密涅瓦就在那里是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.28,0:20:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出发
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.41,0:20:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武装已经全部解除
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.79,0:20:29.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别做无谓的抵抗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.95,0:20:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莉妲小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.42,0:20:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是璞露12
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.50,0:20:35.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不叫什么玛莉妲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.43,0:20:36.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.97,0:20:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么在驾驶那种机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.43,0:20:41.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船长和大伙儿都在担心…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.15,0:20:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许…随便跟我说话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.46,0:20:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我！ 巴纳吉·林克斯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.30,0:20:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当初和舰长…和你的主人一起 在地球…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.74,0:20:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,璞露12 不必理睬他的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.79,0:20:54.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白 主人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.97,0:20:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有状况吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.60,0:20:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机体一切良好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.03,0:20:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在问你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.75,0:21:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍有不适就报告
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.45,0:21:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.40,0:21:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难受的时候别忍着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.42,0:21:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不舒服就告诉我 我会…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.39,0:21:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是命令吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.63,0:21:13.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莉妲小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.30,0:21:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是它
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.77,0:21:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是葛兰雪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.45,0:21:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迦楼罗护卫队正在迎战
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.31,0:21:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打开战斗舰桥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.97,0:21:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不急
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.16,0:22:02.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命加勒特队确认情况
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.07,0:22:06.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任务是把独角兽运抵迦楼罗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.99,0:22:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有必要加入战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.74,0:22:22.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.89,0:22:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉翁那帮家伙 好了伤疤忘了痛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.09,0:22:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各机 保持阵型
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.01,0:22:28.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死死盯住独角兽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.16,0:22:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碍手碍脚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.57,0:22:37.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再把船靠近一点
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.20,0:22:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真要去？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.78,0:22:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进去就是我们的天下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.57,0:22:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 不想想自己一把年纪了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.78,0:23:15.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 这感觉是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.37,0:23:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能让船长和玛莉妲小姐自相残杀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.42,0:23:53.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沃兹
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.32,0:23:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.09,0:23:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.07,0:24:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沃兹！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.51,0:24:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莉妲小姐 听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.16,0:24:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船长来了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.39,0:24:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葛兰雪上的大伙
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.52,0:24:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来救奥黛丽…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.27,0:24:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不杀生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.33,0:24:54.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要强行登舰吗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.63,0:25:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,璞露12！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.37,0:25:12.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,击落迦楼罗号上的飞行踏板
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.35,0:25:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.92,0:25:14.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.85,0:25:19.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以 玛莉妲小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.85,0:25:24.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.26,0:25:25.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉·凯拉姆的护航队干什么吃的？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.01,0:25:27.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全体下降脱离中
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.41,0:25:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在营救坠落僚机
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.93,0:25:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没空陪你们去海面
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.85,0:25:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来这样
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.99,0:25:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是串通好的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.05,0:25:37.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.42,0:25:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴纳吉…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.90,0:25:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.72,0:25:50.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿梭机提前出发 请随我来
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.69,0:26:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人说只要保留驾驶员和机舱
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.37,0:26:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快醒醒
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.80,0:26:12.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的主人…船长不会这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.53,0:26:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和船长之间
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.77,0:26:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不应该成为敌人！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.81,0:26:22.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,璞露…12
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.02,0:26:26.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人是 艾伯特·毕斯特…！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.70,0:26:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,错了！ 你叫玛莉妲
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.31,0:26:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的船长是
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.62,0:26:32.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葛兰雪号的辛尼曼上尉！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.37,0:26:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,璞露12！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.78,0:26:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静下来 只需要听我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.44,0:26:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除此以外全是敌人的花言巧语！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.88,0:26:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回想起来
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.21,0:26:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和船长那么彼此信任…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.99,0:26:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要听他的话
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.28,0:26:52.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高达是你的敌人！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.21,0:26:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把他抓来给我…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.78,0:26:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.36,0:26:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,璞露12
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.79,0:27:01.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舱门关不上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.72,0:27:19.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来接你了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.60,0:27:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.58,0:27:37.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莉妲小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.19,0:27:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高达是…敌人！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.74,0:27:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以 独角兽
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.15,0:27:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别被她影响
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.62,0:27:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍住
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.21,0:28:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快 上DELTA PLUS
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.10,0:28:08.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利迪少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.49,0:28:11.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明白自己是哪边的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.53,0:28:13.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道才这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.71,0:28:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀罗南·马瑟纳斯的儿子是什么后果
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.70,0:28:18.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己明白吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.31,0:28:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴纳吉和独角兽给你
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.68,0:28:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她必须跟我走
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.93,0:28:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么 还不快
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.32,0:28:26.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带我离开这里后
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.62,0:28:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.67,0:28:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离开这里再想也不迟
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.10,0:28:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想保护的是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.92,0:28:35.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我这个人？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.91,0:28:37.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是拉普拉斯之盒的秘密？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.96,0:28:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是家族的…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.70,0:28:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家族什么的无关紧要！
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.59,0:28:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从一百年前拉普拉斯被炸
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.19,0:28:46.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都被搅乱了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.10,0:28:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是 老爸也是
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.28,0:28:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在场的所有人都是
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.12,0:28:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在被那个混乱的结果摆布
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.64,0:28:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不论多么混乱的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.74,0:28:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里住着上百亿人
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.35,0:29:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你无法选择啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.00,0:29:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有去维护它 不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.08,0:29:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能像吉翁那样
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.76,0:29:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来个全部推倒重来
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.26,0:29:08.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.15,0:29:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盒子的秘密必须被保护
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.03,0:29:12.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,密涅瓦大人也明白
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.21,0:29:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才该协助…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.53,0:29:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.82,0:29:17.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切的元凶
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.22,0:29:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你们的宗主！
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.05,0:29:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的宗主…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.79,0:29:25.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赛亚姆·毕斯特得到盒子只是机缘巧合
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.44,0:29:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他暗杀了联邦政府初代首相
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.03,0:29:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并利用人们对此后强权政治的不满壮大势力
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.17,0:29:35.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但吉翁掀起宇宙移民独立运动
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.60,0:29:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年战争爆发
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.16,0:29:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打乱了他的算盘
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.04,0:29:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进入轨道的联邦政府
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.04,0:29:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括铺设轨道的赛亚姆自己
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.13,0:29:45.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到那时才发现
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.82,0:29:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己所作所为的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.20,0:29:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉普拉斯之盒真正的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.82,0:29:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道那些
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.14,0:29:55.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.67,0:29:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个折磨你的盒子
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.92,0:29:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它究竟是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.01,0:30:01.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里在场的所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.46,0:30:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都有权知道
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.29,0:30:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴纳吉
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.91,0:30:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,密涅瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.00,0:30:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我走
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.14,0:30:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,独角兽是危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.17,0:30:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它证明了新人类的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.78,0:30:26.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百年前的祝福即将变成诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.00,0:30:28.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以！
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.43,0:30:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诅咒？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.83,0:30:32.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有改变世界的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.68,0:30:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面对不健全的秩序
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.74,0:30:37.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无力改变它的话 我只有维护
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.68,0:30:38.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.96,0:30:40.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样做可以让你…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.70,0:30:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面来的 注意警戒
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.96,0:30:43.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莎大人
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.71,0:30:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是新吉翁？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.64,0:31:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,密涅瓦！
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.46,0:31:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莉妲小姐 请住手
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.31,0:31:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.88,0:31:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是拯救我的光…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.25,0:31:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都别想夺走它！
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.99,0:31:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.03,0:31:33.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.12,0:31:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不正常
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.24,0:31:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是危险的光
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.58,0:31:39.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在干什么 带密涅瓦回来
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.56,0:31:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里危险
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.40,0:31:43.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,独角兽和报丧女妖发生共鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.61,0:31:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能已经形成了精神力场
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.52,0:31:48.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿克西斯冲击的再现？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.37,0:31:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.92,0:31:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迦楼罗号也难免…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.81,0:32:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葛兰雪就在外面
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.54,0:32:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用这个降落
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.27,0:32:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.28,0:32:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随后就来
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.81,0:32:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请快
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.12,0:32:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样奥黛丽会…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.61,0:32:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全在他控制之下
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.77,0:32:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子竟然能…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.20,0:32:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子…？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.43,0:32:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别动 我这就来
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.14,0:33:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还等什么 快把手伸过来
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.83,0:33:04.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利迪 我和你不是同路人
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.76,0:33:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有空说这些
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.22,0:33:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是扎比家的女性
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.40,0:33:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须看清拉普拉斯之盒的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.50,0:33:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾相信
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.09,0:33:15.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扭曲的秩序也许好过战争…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.55,0:33:19.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但它如果只是令人慢慢窒息
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.39,0:33:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,密涅瓦…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.52,0:33:24.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管父亲和祖父为此犯下滔天大罪
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.87,0:33:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我仍然…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.76,0:33:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算一个人和世界为敌吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.06,0:33:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没人相信世界会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.09,0:33:35.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没人在乎自己死后的世界是什么模样
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.67,0:33:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了他们
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.15,0:33:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不惜得罪他们
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.06,0:33:44.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟有什么值得？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.61,0:33:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.77,0:33:49.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,密涅瓦 不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.32,0:33:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.59,0:33:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会忘记你
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.46,0:33:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,密涅瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.55,0:34:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感应到 巴纳吉
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.01,0:34:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥黛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.12,0:34:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能行吧 独角兽
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.48,0:35:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想办法
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.93,0:35:42.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.23,0:35:45.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗拉斯特 辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.53,0:35:47.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里…
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.85,0:35:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴纳吉
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.89,0:35:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,营救船长和玛莉妲
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.46,0:35:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就靠你了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.62,0:35:52.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.60,0:35:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴纳吉
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.01,0:35:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的声音是那么清晰
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.28,0:35:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太高兴了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.03,0:35:59.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉终于明白
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.68,0:36:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己为什么在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.42,0:36:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你在呼唤我
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.01,0:36:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.73,0:36:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这感觉如果是真实的
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.74,0:36:09.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莉妲小姐肯定也听到了我的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.60,0:36:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定带她回来
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.34,0:36:13.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在这里等着
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.07,0:36:14.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.69,0:36:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.86,0:36:21.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 巴纳吉·林克斯
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.44,0:37:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶的高达们！
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.73,0:37:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是高达吗
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.07,0:37:25.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高达是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.52,0:37:26.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须击败的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.79,0:37:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 玛莉妲小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.56,0:37:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了 冷静下来
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.95,0:37:39.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一字一句喊得人脑袋直响
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.96,0:37:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头痛是因为
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.22,0:37:43.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的你在挣扎
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.19,0:37:47.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是玛莉妲的话听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.83,0:37:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我 辛尼曼
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.82,0:37:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么… 辛尼曼
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.06,0:37:52.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人…
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.69,0:37:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,财团那群畜生
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.91,0:37:56.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对你再调试了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.03,0:37:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莉妲 回来
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.93,0:38:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回来的话 大家都是原样
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.94,0:38:08.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.62,0:38:10.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的主人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.03,0:38:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我女儿 叫玛莉
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.28,0:38:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活着的话 和你年纪相仿
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.48,0:38:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打开舱门从那里下来 玛莉妲
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.35,0:38:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起回天上去
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.71,0:38:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我走
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.41,0:38:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别丢下我一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.65,0:38:47.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这该死的高达
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.99,0:38:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高达 高达
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.97,0:38:54.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高达 高达 高达…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.38,0:38:59.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是高达？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.04,0:39:02.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是…敌人？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.04,0:39:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莉
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.25,0:40:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逆向喷射 60秒倒计时
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.53,0:40:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全舰 准备反加速
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.47,0:40:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耐热伞 准备完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.16,0:40:24.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标脱离迦楼罗 正在上升中
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.01,0:40:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预测汇合坐标 修正误差-8
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.26,0:40:31.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本舰即将接近对流层上层
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.22,0:40:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用系链缆索捕获目标
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.55,0:40:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全体 留意舰船的高度和速度
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.75,0:40:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葛兰雪 黑袖章的伪装货船
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.49,0:40:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是从工业七号开始
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.11,0:40:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我们穷追不舍的那群家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.29,0:40:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样真的合适吗
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.30,0:40:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么合适不合适
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.44,0:40:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是布莱德司令的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.58,0:40:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说 总比无所事事的好
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.61,0:40:55.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,且不论是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.14,0:40:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标 貌似推进力下降
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.19,0:41:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在偏离预定上升曲线
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.55,0:41:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.12,0:41:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.28,0:41:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引擎故障
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.92,0:41:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,功率拉不上去
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.50,0:41:14.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没法子了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.87,0:41:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃料可不够再绕地球一圈
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.05,0:41:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这已经到顶了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.85,0:41:22.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按事先计划
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.16,0:41:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的「老朋友」如期而至
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.47,0:41:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然天上不会掉馅饼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.96,0:41:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是艘被置于联邦和吉翁框架之外的船
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.14,0:41:33.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要抵达
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.44,0:41:34.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道路一定会敞开
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.75,0:41:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.57,0:41:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴纳吉！
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.84,0:41:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,库瓦迪 艾兰 你们在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.38,0:41:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真会蛮干
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.98,0:41:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗拉斯特 有戏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.56,0:41:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在上升…
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.88,0:41:58.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不足以回到轨道
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.38,0:42:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能再降低一点高度吗
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.41,0:42:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到极限了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.47,0:42:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 系链缆索 发射
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.88,0:42:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,系缆 发射
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.98,0:42:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我回天上来 巴纳吉
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.74,0:42:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送到了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.83,0:42:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接上了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.12,0:42:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还…
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.19,0:43:07.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 机体会散架的
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.26,0:43:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴纳吉！
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.11,0:43:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…什么光？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.00,0:44:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高达
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.03,0:45:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方什么来历？
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.53,0:45:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,识别信号匹配
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.39,0:45:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是友军！
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.94,0:45:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炮击来自轨道正面
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.85,0:45:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高度差12 距离400
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.98,0:45:21.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多戈斯基亚级
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.98,0:45:21.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,659)\fnarial\fs26\b0\fsp1}Dogosse Giar
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.26,0:45:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷比尔将军号…！
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.22,0:45:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确定无误吗
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.28,0:45:26.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有错
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.90,0:45:29.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷比尔…将军号
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.32,0:45:31.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机动战士接近 大量！
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.62,0:45:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可是怪物级…
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.00,0:45:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是陷阱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.58,0:45:53.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 从这种部署方式看
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.90,0:45:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拟·阿伽玛也被列为攻击对象
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.95,0:45:58.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想一网打尽吗
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.73,0:45:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.74,0:46:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.27,0:46:06.57,note1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38\fad(300,0)}（燃料用尽）
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.19,0:46:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易…
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.14,0:46:28.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新吉翁？
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.88,0:47:47.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗卢·伏龙特尔…！
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.52,0:47:55.35,note1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38\fad(300,0)}（识别 无匹配）
