Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.76,0:49:14.10,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你须得神采飞扬
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.40,0:49:17.94,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你适合享受孤独
