Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.69,0:49:25.04,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}最好不要再靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.34,0:49:28.79,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我得保持理智
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.94,0:49:32.47,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你明知我不会退让
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.60,0:49:36.23,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)}无人能责备我
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.43,0:49:46.61,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}不要惧怕
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.06,0:49:50.23,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}一切听天由命
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.68,0:49:53.86,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}看看周围
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.32,0:49:57.29,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你就是另一个我
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.88,0:50:01.32,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你是我的女王
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.65,0:50:05.35,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}现在你有何吩咐
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.44,0:50:08.86,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}等待太过漫长
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.98,0:50:12.39,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}谁能给我路标
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.56,0:50:16.20,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你让我懂得了爱
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.30,0:50:19.76,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}谁能给我路标
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.87,0:50:23.38,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我要修正你的规则
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.53,0:50:26.93,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}无人能将你束缚
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.13,0:50:30.89,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你适合享受孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.91,0:50:34.28,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}最好不要再靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.45,0:50:37.90,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}最好不要再靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.06,0:50:41.54,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}不要再回头
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.70,0:50:45.19,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}最好不要再靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.39,0:50:48.61,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}在天塌下来之前
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.66,0:50:57.90,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}归于尘土 渐行渐远
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.09,0:51:05.36,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}却无法将你从我脑中抹去
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.48,0:51:29.29,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}终于明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.46,0:51:32.89,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}自己为何而战
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.34,0:51:36.75,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}直到最后
